apybaras<br></li><li> <strong>Be wary of your shipmates' affinities changing</strong> as hard decisions are made. They may become <strong>your best friends - or your fiercest rivals!</strong></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901890/extras/375af2463bef75843a7247833e4dfb11.poster.avif?t=1657020657\" width=614 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901890/extras/375af2463bef75843a7247833e4dfb11.webm?t=1657020657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901890/extras/375af2463bef75843a7247833e4dfb11.mp4?t=1657020657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901890/extras/3564567a18b8bc41660fc7277d0d1787.poster.avif?t=1657020657\" width=546 height=764 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901890/extras/3564567a18b8bc41660fc7277d0d1787.webm?t=1657020657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>[/url",
